LEVEL ADVANCEMENT TABLES

The following charts show the amount of experience a character must earn in order to gain a level in his character class.  The charts also list the number of spells that a character can have memorized at one time.  Fighters and Thieves can never memorize spells. Remember that all experience earned by a non-human, multiple-class character is divided by the number of classes the character has.  The experience is divided even after the character has reached his maximum level in a particular class.


CLERIC OF GOOD

Level       Experience        Dice
____________________________________

 1          2,000-3,999        2d8
 2          4,000-7,499        3d8
 3          7,500-15,249       4d8
 4          15,250-24,999      5d8
 5          25,000-39,999      6d8
 6          40,000-89,999      7d8
 7          90,000-159,999     8d8
 8          160,000-249,999    9d8

Each level after 8th requires 250,000 experience points and the character gains 1 hit point.


